nodes.text: Nenmo's Curios was a business that was ran by the Toydarian merchant, Nenmo. He ran a stall for it at the Cularin Trade Show aboard the TAV Prosperity, which was held during the Clone Wars. At the stall, he sold various rare but tacky items, including Celebrity Bobble Heads, various datacards, Bantha Smelling Salts, a Dejarik board, and many other items.
